TITLE : cryptoterminal.io
DESCRIPTION :
      These are the available APIs for Cryptoterminal.  You can find  out more about Cryptoterminal at
      [http://cryptoterminal.io](http://cryptoterminal.io)
ENDPOINTS :
    - GET /alert
      Get alerts without any filter (15 per request)
    - GET /alert/coin/{coin}
      filter alerts by coin
    - GET /alert/exchange/{exchange}
      filter alerts by exchange
    - GET /alert/coin/{coin}/{exchange}
      filter alerts by coin and exchange
    - GET /headline
      Get headlines without any filter (15 per request)
    - GET /headline/coin/{coin}
      filter headlines by coin
    - GET /headline/source/{source}
      filter alerts by source
    - GET /headline/search/{searchString}
      filter alerts by search string
    - GET /price/{coin}/{exchange}/{period}
      Get price data for coin by exchange and period

