TITLE : Polygon
DESCRIPTION :
      The future of fintech.
ENDPOINTS :
    - GET /v1/companies
      Available Companies
    - GET /v1/currencies
      Available Currencies
    - GET /v1/historic/agg/{size}/{symbol}/{date}
      Historic Aggregates
    - GET /v1/historic/forex/{from}/{to}/{date}
      Historic Forex Ticks
    - GET /v1/historic/quotes/{symbol}/{date}
      Historic Quotes
    - GET /v1/historic/trades/{symbol}/{date}
      Historic Trades
    - GET /v1/last/currencies/{from}/{to}
      Last Trade for a Currency Pair
    - GET /v1/last/stocks/{symbol}
      Last Trade for a Symbol
    - GET /v1/last_quote/currencies/{from}/{to}
      Last Quote for a Currency Pair
    - GET /v1/last_quote/stocks/{symbol}
      Last Quote for a Symbol

TITLE : CurrencyConversion API
DESCRIPTION :
      This API will fetch currency conversion details from the boss service
ENDPOINTS :
    - GET /get-details/{fromCurrency}
      Get currency conversion details
    - GET /get-ratelist/{fromCurrency}
      Retrieve currency conversion rate list
    - GET /get-list/{currencyCode}
      Get currency conversion list details
